# HTML_CSS
HTML+CSS

/* tr表格行 */
<table>
  <tr>
  </tr>
  <tr>
  </tr>
</table>

/* td表格数据 */
<table>
  <tr>
    <td>73</td>
    <td>81</td>
  </tr>
</table>

/* th表头 */
<table>
  <tr>
    <th></th>
    <th scope="col">Saturday</th>
    <th scope="col">Sunday</th>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <th scope="row">Temperature</th>
    <td>73</td>
    <td>81</td>
  </tr>
</table>

row - this value makes it clear that the heading is for a row.
col - this value makes it clear that the heading is for a column.

/* border */

table, td {
  border: 1px solid black;
}


/* colspan */
<table>
  <tr>
    <th>Monday</th>
    <th>Tuesday</th>
    <th>Wednesday</th>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td colspan="2">Out of Town</td>
    <td>Back in Town</td>
  </tr>
</table>

/* rowspan */
<table>
  <tr> <!-- Row 1 -->
    <th></th>
    <th>Saturday</th>
    <th>Sunday</th>
  </tr>
  <tr> <!-- Row 2 -->
    <th>Morning</th>
    <td rowspan="2">Work</td>
    <td rowspan="3">Relax</td>
  </tr>
  <tr> <!-- Row 3 -->
    <th>Afternoon</th>
  </tr>
  <tr> <!-- Row 4 -->
    <th>Evening</th>
    <td>Dinner</td>
  </tr>
</table>

/*  <tbody>  <thead>  <tfoot>*/

/* font-size */
th, td {
  font-size: 18px;
  font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
  font-weight: 400;
  padding: 20px;
  text-align: left;
  width: 33.3333%;
}

